" Delete trailing spaces and replace Tabs with 2 Spaces
command! FixTrailingSpaces :let _s=@/<Bar>:%s/\s*\r\?$//e<Bar>:%s/\t/  /e<Bar>:let @/=_s<Bar>:nohl

